about.summary: Statistical Data and Metadata eXchange (SDMX) for the Python data ecosystem

name: pandasdmx
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pandaSDMX" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 799d53f8c8a49321fc92d8bf0f6bf7101b0ffe14c7f2768aef33776b7eae48f6

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv" 

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - flit >=2.3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - lxml >=3.6
    - pandas >=0.24
    - pydantic >=1.1
    - requests >=2.7

test:
  imports:
    - pandasdmx
    - pandasdmx.reader.sdmxml
    - pandasdmx.writer
    
about:
  home: "https://github.com/dr-leo/pandasdmx"
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE 
  summary: "Statistical Data and Metadata eXchange (SDMX) for the Python data ecosystem"
  doc_url: "https://pandasdmx.readthedocs.io/" 
  dev_url: "https://github.com/dr-leo/pandasdmx" 

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dr-leo
